    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 11th level, you may select any minor binding vow of your choice.</p><p> You gain this vow's benefits but none of it's drawbacks.</p><p> A vow gained this way does not cost any slots.</p><p> Additionally, you reduce any falling damage taken by five times your level.</p><p> Finally, while you are in the air, you may make any movements that would normally require you to be on solid ground.</p><p></p>",
